{"tid":967304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國同香港嘅女權婦團無哂影】印度神廟首向所有婦女開放遭阻撓","createTime":"2019-01-03T11:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T00:33:26.000Z","uid":54337,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94ec7aaf371d78b385bbfbe322911060effbfc8f","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"印度神廟首向所有婦女開放遭阻撓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181018/20524505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181018%2F20524505&d=fKH14PBUn4xEMhEcuLN8vF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=fe605b61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181018%2F20524505&h=4336eab3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181018/20524505</a>"},{"pid":"8181a654aa547bf33b61485f06f80749fbabce87","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"印度最高法院7月裁定，印度教知名朝聖地、南部喀拉拉邦深山的薩巴里馬拉神廟（Sabarimala Shrine）不可禁止10至50歲女性入廟，神廟遂由昨日起開放讓所有婦女進場。示威者昨日向到場戒備的警員擲石，警員出動警棍還擊，多人受傷，包括兩名女記者。<br />\n<br />\n宗教狂熱者查車恐嚇<br />\n<br />\n薩巴里馬拉神廟建於12世紀前，每年吸引4,500萬人次造訪。神廟昨起舉行為期五天的每月祭祀法會，也是法院裁決後首次對外開放。印度教相信女性經期「不潔」，會褻瀆廟內供奉的獨身神明阿雅帕（Lord Ayyappa），故神廟禁止10歲到50歲女性入場，直至7月才被高院以平權為由推翻。<br />\n不過，宗教狂熱者和右翼政黨連日在廟外抗議，包括總理穆迪所屬的印度人民黨（BJP）。神廟開放前一天，反對者更在神廟約20公里外的尼拉卡爾（Nilakkal）攔截車輛，向車內女乘客強索身份證明，一發現有10歲到50歲女性就阻止她們前進。他們認為廢除禁令等於破壞傳統並傷害信徒情感，早前神廟總祭司坦特里亦警告，女性若一意孤行入場隨時引發暴力衝突：「虔誠信徒不會強行破壞2,100年來的規矩，女性可到其他廟宇祭拜阿雅帕。」被視為激進派的濕婆神軍（Shiv Sena）甚至威脅婦女踏入神廟將形同「大規模自殺」。婦解代表潘特就反問：「男人憑甚麼管制女人可以或不可去哪裏？」<br />\n喀拉拉邦總督維加揚曾公開保證，沒一個參加法會的信徒會被阻進場，並警告將對那些破壞法律的人採取嚴厲行動。<br />\n美聯社/法新社"},{"pid":"6d71d336c1daf98bc54401fd7f1c436810d43075","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"成日話男女平等嘅美國同香港女權婦團呢？<br />\n唔出聲支持印度女人爭取權益？<br />\n香港婦團呢？香港女權分子呢？<br />\n唔遊行去印度領使館，拉橫額遞信，聲援印度女人？"},{"pid":"d13a2d525ee40ae02170fa9f1a3f2ada68dad9e5","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:46:13.000Z","msg":"弱智女權人士 105 ，我等緊你入嚟"},{"pid":"040e0d88a9cd9f2bb7ac80cf2ec0916370cde672","tid":967304,"uid":9542,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6d71d336c1daf98bc54401fd7f1c436810d43075","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"成日話男女平等嘅美國同香港女權婦團呢？<br />\n唔出聲支持印度女人爭取權益？<br />\n香港婦團呢？香港女權分子呢？<br />\n唔遊行去印度領使館，拉橫額遞信，聲援印度女人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"你唔好咁痴線啦"},{"pid":"f2ab420a189bddbc8729f3c9123cacee7260beec","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:01:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181203/s00002/1543774969759/%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E8%95%A9%E5%A9%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8D-%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4metoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181203%2Fs00002%2F1543774969759%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2595%25A9%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258D-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4metoo&d=fKH14PBUn4xEMhEcuLN8vF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=07d047fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181203%2Fs00002%2F1543774969759%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2595%25A9%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258D-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4metoo&h=cf562a75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181203/s00002/1543774969759/%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E8%95%A9%E5%A9%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8D-%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4metoo</a><br />\n<br />\n港「蕩婦遊行」 百人聲援MeToo<br />\n2018/12/3<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】鼓勵性騷擾或性侵犯受害者勇敢發聲的「#MeToo」運動一年前席捲全球，而上月本港一宗前教練涉嫌非禮女學員案，被告非禮罪名不成立。去年被BBC評為全球百大女性之一的Angie Ng認為，上述案件判決令人失望，而該受害人隨即在網上被人抨擊責備，顯示社會有部分人不理解性暴力受害人。因此，她昨午發起香港「蕩婦遊行」（Slut Walk），聲援性暴力受害人，反擊「Victim-blaming（責備受害者）」風氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美先進國家，有女權搞slut walk，香港女權婦團就跟到足。<br />\n印度係發展中國家，印度女人爭取女權，香港女權婦團呢？扮睇唔到，乜聲都無。<br />\n<br />\n乜印度女人唔係女人咩？男女平權嘛。印度女人爭取同印度男人有同樣權力，香港婦團唔去聲援嘅？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哎喲喲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24edc8d586273c2d0d2052749167898fc0c17cf6","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:15:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n柴田妹<br />\n月野兔兔<br />\n西摩西陵<br />\n鄧鏡波<br />\nDCP-J105<br />\nAndyH</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a7e6c1fd39eb8f679f93799338ce496b6e8a1c61","tid":967304,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"婦解代表潘特就反問：「男人憑甚麼管制女人可以或不可去哪裏？」<br />\n<br />\n宗教自由<br />\n你係信教嘅就應該知自己不潔，唔應該入去。<br />\n你唔信教嘅，點解要入人神廟？<br />\n<br />\n結論：想入去嘅都不懷好意"},{"pid":"5438ef10920ee513f7decdf710b154d07f5b8d47","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f2ab420a189bddbc8729f3c9123cacee7260beec","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:01:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181203/s00002/1543774969759/%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E8%95%A9%E5%A9%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8D-%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4metoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181203%2Fs00002%2F1543774969759%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2595%25A9%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258D-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4metoo&d=fKH14PBUn4xEMhEcuLN8vF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=07d047fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20181203%2Fs00002%2F1543774969759%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2595%25A9%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258D-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4metoo&h=cf562a75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20181203/s00002/1543774969759/%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E8%95%A9%E5%A9%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8D-%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4metoo</a><br />\n<br />\n港「蕩婦遊行」 百人聲援MeToo<br />\n2018/12/3<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】鼓勵性騷擾或性侵犯受害者勇敢發聲的「#MeToo」運動一年前席捲全球，而上月本港一宗前教練涉嫌非禮女學員案，被告非禮罪名不成立。去年被BBC評為全球百大女性之一的Angie Ng認為，上述案件判決令人失望，而該受害人隨即在網上被人抨擊責備，顯示社會有部分人不理解性暴力受害人。因此，她昨午發起香港「蕩婦遊行」（Slut Walk），聲援性暴力受害人，反擊「Victim-blaming（責備受害者）」風氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美先進國家，有女權搞slut walk，香港女權婦團就跟到足。<br />\n印度係發展中國家，印度女人爭取女權，香港女權婦團呢？扮睇唔到，乜聲都無。<br />\n<br />\n乜印度女人唔係女人咩？男女平權嘛。印度女人爭取同印度男人有同樣權力，香港婦團唔去聲援嘅？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哎喲喲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"歐美女權運動，先進國家搞平權運動，香港女權婦團就跟足，就代表潮，代表型。上鏡，上位，打卡，拎道德光環，自我感覺良好。<br />\n<br />\n印度女權運動，errrr，蠻夷地區，關我乜事先。於是，香港女權婦團，就屁都唔放一個，扮睇唔到，無聲氣。<br />\n<br />\n此之謂香港女權人士。<br />\n根本係虛偽、人盡可夫、不知所謂嘅仆街"},{"pid":"4b4b466f9869791fb513c70b718705fa2d96e00d","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.imgur.com/YSkoirt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYSkoirt.jpg&h=7a76339c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人呢？<br />\n去左邊呀？<br />\n歐美有slut walk，就去跟足，因為跟歐美 = 型、潮、拎光環。<br />\n印度女人唔係女人咩？印度女人無同印度男人擁有同樣嘅權利？<br />\n今次唔見你出嚟聲援？"},{"pid":"f11ea32bb3754a3e5f6063e2e18ee61d7e23edbc","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/photo/bkn-20181202163028606-1202_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181202183057\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181202%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181202163028606-1202_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181202183057&h=334946ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認清楚呢班人，睇清楚佢地嘅嘴臉，<br />\n這群人，兩個字：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">虛偽</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bb9d3759e884e45dafb1b6295feadac282c53ce7","tid":967304,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"咁香港本土派需唔需要去支持一下中國民主呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e0ed0008aa76ec848a16caedcc055b25413347","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"弱智105<br />\n我等你<br />\n你入嚟啦<br />\n如果你仲有膽的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb624b8c131444b7aaac5f30baf241620e50c8e7","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f11ea32bb3754a3e5f6063e2e18ee61d7e23edbc","tid":967304,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/photo/bkn-20181202163028606-1202_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181202183057\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h